name: Black Unicorn Corp.
description: Moon on Ethereum (MOON) is a utility-focused memecoin developed on the Ethereum blockchain. The project combines the appeal of memecoins with real-world benefits for its holders, creating a unique value proposition. As a community-driven token, MOON is designed to foster engagement and provide tangible rewards for its users, supported by a robust liquidity pool and consistent market activity. The total supply of MOON is capped at 13.5 billion tokens, all of which are in circulation. The project boasts a market capitalization of $37.8 million and liquidity of $2.1 million, ensuring a stable trading environment. With 3,610 holders and over 1,340 transactions to date, MOON has gained significant traction since its pool creation on December 14, 2024. Key utilities of MOON include its role in incentivizing community participation and enabling decentralized trading activities.
